						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone standing in the Sōmaliṅga temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>12th-13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th-13th Century A.D.,</hi> refers to the death of a hero during a cattle raid, at Mudunīru. It mentions <hi rend="bold">Bamma-nṛipāḷa.</hi></p>						

